4.  OIOC J/1/19, f. 225.
5. Bengal Past and Present, xxiv (1922), 114, 124.
6.  P. Philip, British Residents at the Cape, 115; PROB 11/2220/834.
7. Holland Jnl. i. 236.
8.  OIOC J/1/18, ff. 294-8.
9. Ann. Reg. (1817), Chron. pp. 432-49 contains a full account of the shipwreck extracted from John McLeod’s Voyage of the Alceste (1817).
10.  B. O’Meara, Napoleon in Exile, ii. 404-6.
