            Property Description
    


Let the sunshine in on this light and bright turn key Canyon Gate home, ready for immediate move in! Apprx 2508 sq feet of neutral charm, high vaulted ceilings, laminate & tile flooring downstairs and carpet upstairs. Upon entry into the home, you will find a private office that can possibly be converted into a 4th bedroom. Cook's kitchen with abundance of granite counter space overlooking family room. All three bedrooms found upstairs outlining a spacious open loft. 3 car tandem garage with epoxy flooring. Park like backyard with dog run, water fountain, miniature vegetable garden, and mature fruit trees overlooking unobstructed 180 degree mountain views. Home is located close to award winning schools, shopping, and freeway. This beauty won't last! Come see to appreciate.

